# Revenue Operations & Customer Churn Analysis
## 📊 GG Socials Strategy Case Study

### Executive Summary
This project analyzes a dataset of over 7,000 customers to identify revenue leakage and retention opportunities. By linking behavioral data (Last Login) with financial data (Total Revenue), I identified a **$10.5M revenue core** and developed a 3-tier retention strategy to mitigate a **20% early-stage churn risk.**

